data.description: All the big ticket items are taken care of!!  NEW ROOF, 1 y/o WATER HEATER and HVAC system!  Come see this WARM and COZY home! Close to City Center!   This beautiful 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home is ready for a new owner! This well cared for the home has custom colors and upgrades throughout,  kitchen that opens to the living space along with a home office.  Enjoy the evenings out on your covered patio. Close to the community pool and park! GREAT SPRING schools and LOW taxes! This one is a must see! HVAC system was replaced in June of this year!
